snippet.title: Arcade Archives Armed F
snippet.description:
"Armed F" is a shooting game released by Nihon Bussan in 1988.
Equip the armor that can execute various types of attacks to fight in several worlds like the insect stage and the machine stage.
You can also reverse the armor to change the formation for defeating enemies in a wide range.


Arcade Archives Official Website
http://www.hamster.co.jp/american_hamster/arcadearchives/
